data.name: lblMainWindowPage.Text
data.value: You can configure if any info will be shown in the window title and in what order. Choose what skills will be shown in your characters monitors skill list and their highlighted status. Display or not the overview tab and select the info to be shown.

data.name: lblRelocatorPage.Text
data.value: "Show Relocator Menu" enables you to manually relocate any EVE windows that fits in your screens. When checking "Enable Automatic Relocation" and EVEMon is running, it automatically relocates any EVE window that fits exactly to any of your screens. You can manually select whenever this checking will occur.
